snippet.title: The Simpsons: Return of the Space Mutants (NES Swamp Thing Hack) Full Play Through
snippet.description:
me playing through The Simpsons: Return of the Space Mutants. this game is a hack of Swamp Thing using Simpson sprites that i bought from UncleTusk.com. honestly, it actually brightens up the game and it wasn't too bad of a play through. i took 1 death at the final boss. i am sorry about that. everything else is pretty clean. thank you for watching!
if you would like to hear some commentary regarding this game, feel free to check out my no death play through of Swamp Thing. pretty much everything i said over there is my same thoughts for this game since they are essentially the same game. https://youtu.be/sVcY9-ZAC9c
